==Problem editing pages on Firefox with KeeFox (solved) ==

When I tried to edit a page in Firefox, it would show the correct page's text briefly, then refresh immediately to show the text for DocString. 

It turned out to be due to KeeFox interacting oddly with the form - I had an entry for emacswiki.org with just my username, but when I removed the entry I could edit the page okay. No more switching to Chrome...

-- BrianBurns 2015-12-07

